"},{"pid":"8a7e417554dee56aa0e3bed5d4d7158f539e1410","tid":86361,"uid":2510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T05:53:59.000Z","msg":"值錢？每日痾兩分鐘，痾五日已經唔洗再返，假就有排你放了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221d9f97b168a57a1f8b9bad66fa04a9704c22d0","tid":86361,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T05:54:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>痾屎基本都30分鐘。。。</blockquote><br />\n無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時一日兩次</blockquote><br />\n屙尿另計~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7dd64699adbaa0f9b5b0bbfea7fd6498415a40","tid":86361,"uid":11721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T06:00:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>痾屎基本都30分鐘。。。</blockquote><br />\n冗員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我柯一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n救生員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a62b2a5c692ce624d506f657b6929cdeeeae1c","tid":86361,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T06:07:38.000Z","msg":"食完早餐屙<br />\n岩岩食完lunch 又屙"},{"pid":"c6f8fa7fd7b5532b46ac231ebff74513a6dcb48d","tid":86361,"uid":45,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T06:08:33.000Z","msg":"宜家就係痾住上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe918dac0a7b8851c81c8d45366b3a06719e876","tid":86361,"uid":2777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T06:16:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a50160da813c5070293b0aa2d77b7250e1eaad9","tid":86361,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T06:33:31.000Z","msg":"10分鐘咁少？<br />\n做office 最緊要學識行為偽術<br />\n去廁所一日total 唔好少過30min <br />\n淨係洗手都要跟足醫生指引 20 秒洗一隻<br />\n<br />\n去茶水間沖茶沖咖啡 沖乜柒都好<br />\n洗杯要洗得乾淨過內科醫生 再幫水機啲水撳返加熱<br />\n啲水唔熱 點沖嘢飲呀？<br />\n<br />\n做盡以上行為嘅話一日起碼都一個鐘 <br />\n仲未計食飯同飯氣攻心好眼訓唔願郁時段<br />\n為咗消除大眾疑慮 喺office行嗰陣唔好慢吞吞<br />\n多啲同人打招呼 出入幫手撳吓lift <br />\n讓人出先呢啲已經係基本步驟<br />\n<br />\n有心就得閒讚人兩句 樣好嘅就讚吓個樣 <br />\n樣唔好嘅就讚吓件衫<br />\n至於兩樣都冇嘅 咪讚吓佢隻杯囉<br />\n喂 你隻杯幾趣絰過 邊撚到買架？<br />\n<br />\n做個盡責嘅冗員 人人有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32dfb97c7f7c8269679c8447429d13adc683d76","tid":86361,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T06:56:02.000Z","msg":"我一日去六次廁所，每次十分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efea63c5e2313017d9f10f4cccbbef20c63ba8d0","tid":86361,"uid":35069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:05:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>痾屎基本都30分鐘。。。</blockquote><br />\n無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時一日兩次</blockquote><br />\n屎忽窿都涼乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e78032aeb341774309f3353c63db6ddc29021e7","tid":86361,"uid":24105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:07:44.000Z","msg":"痾住屎睇到呢個post<br />\n痾緊今日第二篤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4964c74537c2902b38c962000066529f2955b052","tid":86361,"uid":58796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:10:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>痾屎基本都30分鐘。。。</blockquote><br />\n無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時一日兩次</blockquote><br />\n計埋我食煙食早餐<b